n single-letter upper bound by Liang et al. that has a\nmin-max form. The proof of the upper bound uses a novel distribution coupling\nargument.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jan 2016 16:50:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Aug 2016 10:33:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2016 09:15:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-19"}
