or of the Standard Model as well as\nextensions including ${\\rm U}(1)$ gauge interactions, such as asymmetric dark\nmatter models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jan 2016 22:50:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 May 2016 19:08:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-12"}
